metadata.description: Total fertility rate with correlation analysis of socioeconomic factors
metadata.note: Correlation does not imply causation. Multiple factors interact in complex ways.
metadata.methodology: Pearson correlation coefficients calculated over overlapping time periods (1990-2024). Some factors use estimated data from official publications where direct API access is unavailable.
